reviews.review_text:
Magnificent Audience Recording Even with a few flips, etc., and a generation down this show is a world beater. This is a magnificent audience recording. Thanks, Jason Flair.

Band's performance is cohesive and energetic.

A grate night to be. A live.
A good, not great, show; not a very great recording, but better than any of the others.
